   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>"Year 22 of Antoninus Caesar the Lord, Mesore the 5th intercalary day. (Give) from the account of Tiberius Julius Theon and Tiberius Julius Theon, alias Tryphon, to Diogenes the praktor, for his salary in the month Mesore thirty-two drachmas, total 32 drachmas. (2nd hd.) Give the 32 drachmas."</ab>
         </div>
